post_text: Due to the current changes in our community with the dismissal of schools and potential work shortage related to the COVID-19 pandemic from now until April 13th all uninsured children who are currently patients of Danville Pediatrics and Primary Care will have provider fees waived for sick visits at Danville Pediatrics and Primary Care. Our goal during this time is to ensure that every Danville Pediatrics patient that needs care can receive it regardless of ability to pay.

Are you a nurse looking for a change in your career? Come join our team!

There is a RN/ LPN position available at Danville High School through the Danville Independent School system.

Please visit the district website, to apply - www.danvilleschools.net
